SUMMARY:Closure: RODING VALLEY STATION: From Tuesday 6 May until end of 
 July 2025\, westbound trains (towards Woodford) will not stop at the 
 station and the footbridge will be closed. Access to and exit from the 
 station will be via Station Way only. Please travel via eastbound trains 
 and change at Chigwell\, or for step-free access\, change at Hainault or 
 use local London Buses route W14 to Woodford.
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR